Per-phase envelope contract snippet (pattern to add to each phase)



Add these fields to each phase object (wherever phases live in your template):


{
  "validation_evidence_path": "evidence/phase/{phase_id}/io_validation.json",
  "envelope_contract": {
    "required_input_envelopes": [
      { "schema_id": "acms.artifact_envelope.v1", "artifact_schema": "acms.plan_input.v1" }
    ],
    "produced_output_envelopes": [
      { "schema_id": "acms.artifact_envelope.v1", "artifact_schema": "acms.phase_output.v1" }
    ],
    "derived_from_artifacts_policy": {
      "require_paths": true,
      "require_sha256": true,
      "allow_empty": false
    }
  }
}


Notes:


artifact_schema is intentionally separate from the envelope schema (envelope is transport; artifact_schema is payload type).

allow_empty=false enforces LIV usefulness (no fake lineage).



