Watcher contract (PowerShell behavior spec you can implement verbatim)



These are the non-negotiable behaviors the watcher must implement to remain deterministic:


Create a run request file under INBOX_PLANS\.queue\ using an atomic write:
write to *.tmp then rename to *.json

Queue item content:
run_request_id, created_at, plan_path, plan_sha256, mode

Process queue FIFO by filename sort (stable ordering).

For each request:
invoke orchestrator with explicit args (--plan-path, --run-root-base, --mode headless)

read orchestrator’s emitted run_summary.json to decide success/fail

move the plan to ARCHIVE_PLANS\{run_id}\ or FAILED_PLANS\{run_id}\

Never delete evidence or logs. Never overwrite an existing {run_id} dir.


